\p 
\v 7 \w Therefore|strong="G1352"\w*—\w just|strong="G2531"\w* \w as|strong="G2531"\w* \w the|strong="G3588"\w* \w Holy|strong="G4151"\w* \w Spirit|strong="G4151"\w* \w says|strong="G3004"\w*:\f + \fr 3:7 \ft The author is affirming that Psalm 95 was inspired by the Holy Spirit.\f*
\q1 “\w Today|strong="G4594"\w*, \w if|strong="G1437"\w* \w you|strong="G1437"\w* \w would|strong="G1437"\w* \w hear|strong="G5456"\w* \w His|strong="G3588"\w* \w voice|strong="G5456"\w*,
