\v 5 \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w serve|strong="G3000"\w* \w a|strong="G2532"\w* \w copy|strong="G5262"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w shadow|strong="G4639"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w heavenly|strong="G2032"\w* \w things|strong="G3956"\w*\f + \fr 8:5 \ft The Tabernacle assembled by Moses was but a ‘shadow’ of the real thing; which probably means that the spiritual realm is more ‘real’ than the physical one—which is difficult for us to believe, so very few live on that basis.\f* (\w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w why|strong="G1063"\w* \w Moses|strong="G3475"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* \w warned|strong="G5537"\w* \w by|strong="G1722"\w* \w God|strong="G5537"\w* \w when|strong="G2532"\w* \w he|strong="G2532"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* \w ready|strong="G3195"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* assemble \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w Tabernacle|strong="G4633"\w*: “\w See|strong="G3708"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w*,” \w He|strong="G2532"\w* \w says|strong="G5346"\w*, “\w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w* \w make|strong="G4160"\w* \w everything|strong="G3956"\w* \w according|strong="G2596"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w pattern|strong="G5179"\w* \w shown|strong="G1166"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w* \w on|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w mountain|strong="G3735"\w*”)—
